":ref:`Target Build Specification Properties <Target Build Specification>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2497
msgid ""
"These evaluate as a :ref:`semicolon-separated list <CMake Language Lists>` "
"representing the union of the value on the target itself with the values of "
"the corresponding :ref:`Target Usage Requirements` on targets named by the "
"target's :prop_tgt:`LINK_LIBRARIES`:"
