#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2502
msgid ""
"For :ref:`Target Compile Properties`, evaluation of corresponding usage "
"requirements is transitive over the closure of the linked targets' :prop_tgt:"
"`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES` *excluding* entries guarded by the :genex:"
"`LINK_ONLY` generator expression."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2507
msgid ""
"For :ref:`Target Link Properties`, evaluation of corresponding usage "
"requirements is transitive over the closure of the linked targets' :prop_tgt:"
"`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES` *including* entries guarded by the :genex:"
"`LINK_ONLY` generator expression.  See policy :policy:`CMP0166`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2514
msgid ""
"Evaluation of :prop_tgt:`LINK_LIBRARIES` itself is now transitive. See "
"policy :policy:`CMP0189`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2517
msgid ":ref:`Target Usage Requirement Properties <Target Usage Requirements>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2518
msgid ""
"These evaluate as a :ref:`semicolon-separated list <CMake Language Lists>` "
"representing the union of the value on the target itself with the values of "
"the same properties on targets named by the target's :prop_tgt:"
"`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES`:"
