#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2523
msgid ""
"For :ref:`Transitive Compile Properties`, evaluation is transitive over the "
"closure of the target's :prop_tgt:`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES` *excluding* "
"entries guarded by the :genex:`LINK_ONLY` generator expression."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2527
msgid ""
"For :ref:`Transitive Link Properties`, evaluation is transitive over the "
"closure of the target's :prop_tgt:`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES` *including* "
"entries guarded by the :genex:`LINK_ONLY` generator expression. See policy :"
"policy:`CMP0166`."
