"``PROP``, named without an ``INTERFACE_`` prefix, checks the :prop_tgt:"
"`TRANSITIVE_COMPILE_PROPERTIES` and :prop_tgt:`TRANSITIVE_LINK_PROPERTIES` "
"properties on target ``tgt``, on targets named by its :prop_tgt:"
"`LINK_LIBRARIES`, and on the transitive closure of targets named by the "
"linked targets' :prop_tgt:`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES`."
