#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2550
msgid ""
"If ``PROP`` is listed by one of those properties, then it evaluates as a :"
"ref:`semicolon-separated list <CMake Language Lists>` representing the union "
"of the value on the target itself with the values of the corresponding "
"``INTERFACE_PROP`` on targets named by the target's :prop_tgt:"
