msgid ""
"If ``PROP`` is named by :prop_tgt:`TRANSITIVE_COMPILE_PROPERTIES`, "
"evaluation of the corresponding ``INTERFACE_PROP`` is transitive over the "
"closure of the linked targets' :prop_tgt:`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES`, "
"excluding entries guarded by the :genex:`LINK_ONLY` generator expression."
