"transitive closure of targets named by its :prop_tgt:"
"`INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/cmake-generator-expressions.7.rst:2573
msgid ""
"If the corresponding ``PROP`` is listed by one of those properties, then "
"``INTERFACE_PROP`` evaluates as a :ref:`semicolon-separated list <CMake "
